# 3. What properties are assigned to heat exchanger primary flow-in temperature sensor?

PREFIX sosa: <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX hpcc: <http://example.org/hpcc#>
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/individuals#>

SELECT ?property ?value
WHERE {  
  ex:HeatExchangerPrimaryFlowInTemperatureSensor ?property ?value ;
  
}
